OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family
OL,4,Cjailed for exploiting servants
OL,6,FFour members of Britain's richest
OL,7,Ffamily have been handed prison
OL,8,Fsentences in Switzerland for
OL,9,Fexploiting servants working in their
OL,10,Fluxury villa.
OL,12,FPrakash Hinduja and his wife, Kamal,
OL,13,Fwere jailed for four and a half years
OL,14,Feach, while their son, Ajay, and his
OL,15,Fwife, Namrata, both received four
OL,16,Fyears in prison.
