OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family
OL,4,Cjailed for exploiting servants
OL,6,FThey banned the workers, mostly
OL,7,Filliterate and from India, from
OL,8,Fleaving the villa and forced them to
OL,9,Fwork excruciatingly long days,
OL,10,Fsometimes up to 18 hours.
OL,12,FThe court found the four guilty of
OL,13,Fexploiting the workers, paying them
OL,14,Fwages less than a tenth of the income
OL,15,Ffor domestic work in Switzerland.
OL,17,FThe Hindujas were not found guilty of
OL,18,Fcharges of trafficking, on the grounds
OL,19,Fthe staff in part understood what they
OL,20,Fwere getting into.
