OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family
OL,4,Cjailed for exploiting servants
OL,6,FThe family topped this year's Sunday
OL,7,FTimes Rich List of the United
OL,8,FKingdom's wealthiest people, with a
OL,9,Fnet worth of around #37.2 billion.
OL,11,FThey did not attend court, but a fifth
OL,12,Fdefendent - the family's business
OL,13,Fmanager Najib Ziazi - was present, and
OL,14,Freceived an 18-month suspended
OL,15,Fsentence.
OL,17,FEmployees slept in the basement of the
OL,18,Fvilla, in the Cologny neighbourhood of
OL,19,FGeneva, and said Kamal Hinduja
OL,20,Finstilled a "climate of fear".
