OL,3,CFour of Britain's richest family
OL,4,Cjailed for exploiting servants
OL,6,FThey also had their passports seized
OL,7,Fand were paid with rupees into banks
OL,8,Fback home that they could not access.
OL,10,FThe Hindujas moved to Switzerland in
OL,11,Fthe late 1980s. Prakash Hinduja was
OL,12,Fconvicted on less serious but similar
OL,13,Fcharges in 2007.
OL,15,FAlong with three of of his brothers,
OL,16,FPrakash Hinduja is a leader of an
OL,17,Findustrial conglomerate in sectors
OL,18,Fincluding information technology,
OL,19,Fmedia, power, real estate and
OL,20,Fhealthcare.
